It is to exercise the power of regular expressions in information searching.  
Write a Python code that reads in each abstract and extract the abstract identity (‘File’), NSF organization (‘NSF org’), 
the award amount, and abstract text. Please submit the output with a tabular format included.  
Distribution of sentence lengths to identify sentences in the abstract. May use sentence tokenizers in Python.  
Output should contain the abstract identity, the sentence number, and the sentence text delimited with a bar (|),  
and the total number of sentences per each file at the end. 
